---
title: Spiced Double Chicken & Cos Walnut Salad with Dijon Hollandaise
description: If you think this is a normal chicken and cos lettuce salad then think again! This version is bursting with pleasant
surprises like walnuts for a sweet crunch and a dijon hollandaise dressing because we can’t get enough of this punchy
flavour combo. Chicken salad has now been upgraded to special level.

